                            <comment id="14174294" author="thobbs" created="Thu, 16 Oct 2014 21:39:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://datastax-oss.atlassian.net/browse/PYTHON-173&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;PYTHON-173&lt;/a&gt; is the cause.  I&apos;m guessing this is not related to &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-8012&quot; title=&quot;cqlsh &amp;quot;DESCRIBE KEYSPACES;&amp;quot; returns empty after upgrade&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-8012&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-8012&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
